<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<%- include('partials/head') %>
<body>
    <%- include('partials/header') %>
    <main>
        <div class="container-custom py-10 md:py-16">
            <section class="style-shell px-6 py-8 md:px-10 md:py-12">
                <div class="pointer-events-none absolute inset-0">
                    <div class="absolute right-[-3rem] top-[-2rem] h-40 w-40 rounded-full bg-gold/20 blur-3xl"></div>
                    <div class="absolute bottom-[-3rem] left-[-2rem] h-52 w-52 rounded-full bg-accent-purple/15 blur-3xl"></div>
                </div>

                <div class="relative z-10 grid gap-10 lg:grid-cols-[1.02fr_0.98fr] lg:items-center">
                    <div>
                        <span class="style-kicker mb-6">Ancient wisdom, modern delivery</span>
                        <h1 class="title font-cormorant text-5xl text-accent-purple font-medium leading-[0.92] md:text-7xl">Vagus Skool</h1>
                        <p class="subtitle mt-4 font-cormorant text-2xl text-gold leading-tight md:text-3xl">Discover the Ancient Wisdom of Ultra Breath</p>
                        <p class="mt-6 max-w-2xl text-lg leading-relaxed text-dark-text/85 md:text-xl">
                            Experience the extraordinary power of Ultra Breath, a revolutionary practice combining ultrasound-enhanced vagus nerve stimulation with ancient Tummo breathing techniques.
                        </p>

                        <div class="mt-8 grid gap-3 sm:grid-cols-2">
                            <div class="style-metric">
                                <p class="section-label">Practice</p>
                                <p class="mt-3 text-lg text-dark-text/85">Master the 30-breath technique with a calmer, more focused daily ritual.</p>
                            </div>
                            <div class="style-metric">
                                <p class="section-label">Outcome</p>
                                <p class="mt-3 text-lg text-dark-text/85">Activate your vagus nerve and access deeper states of regulation.</p>
                            </div>
                        </div>

                        <div class="mt-8 flex flex-wrap gap-3">
                            <span class="style-chip">Release natural acetylcholine</span>
                            <span class="style-chip">Build nervous system resilience</span>
                            <span class="style-chip">Learn at your own pace</span>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <div class="video-shell p-3">
                        <div class="relative pb-[56.25%] h-0 overflow-hidden rounded-[1.25rem] shadow-2xl">
                            <iframe
                                class="absolute top-0 left-0 h-full w-full"
                                src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/kozJJDl8nJ0?si=vJKEXayc3p_hNMx1"
                                title="YouTube video player"
                                frameborder="0"
                                allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share"
                                referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin"
                                allowfullscreen>
                            </iframe>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </section>

            <section class="mt-8 grid gap-6 lg:grid-cols-[1.1fr_0.9fr]">
                <article class="section-shell">
                    <p class="section-label">What you will experience</p>
                    <div class="mt-6 grid gap-4 md:grid-cols-2">
                        <div class="style-panel">
                            <h2 class="font-cormorant text-3xl text-accent-purple">Guided regulation</h2>
                            <p class="mt-3 text-dark-text/80">Learn a simple, direct method for calming the body and training your system toward safety.</p>
                        </div>
                        <div class="style-panel">
                            <h2 class="font-cormorant text-3xl text-accent-purple">Embodied practice</h2>
                            <p class="mt-3 text-dark-text/80">Turn theory into breathwork, ritual, and repeatable daily action you can actually sustain.</p>
                        </div>
                        <div class="style-panel">
                            <h2 class="font-cormorant text-3xl text-accent-purple">Deeper awareness</h2>
                            <p class="mt-3 text-dark-text/80">Use modern vagus nerve concepts to better understand stress, energy, and inner balance.</p>
                        </div>
                        <div class="style-panel">
                            <h2 class="font-cormorant text-3xl text-accent-purple">Community momentum</h2>
                            <p class="mt-3 text-dark-text/80">Move with a group of people exploring similar healing, breathwork, and nervous system practices.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </article>

                <aside class="section-shell">
                    <p class="section-label">Live offer</p>
                    <div class="mt-5 rounded-[1.75rem] bg-accent-purple px-6 py-8 text-center text-soft-white shadow-xl">
                        <p class="text-sm uppercase tracking-[0.28em] text-white/65">Special offer ends in</p>
                        <div id="countdown" class="mt-6 flex justify-center gap-6 md:gap-8">
                            <div class="flex flex-col items-center">
                                <span id="minutes" class="text-4xl font-bold text-gold md:text-5xl">05</span>
                                <span class="text-sm uppercase tracking-wider text-white/70">Minutes</span>
                            </div>
                            <div class="flex flex-col items-center">
                                <span id="seconds" class="text-4xl font-bold text-gold md:text-5xl">00</span>
                                <span class="text-sm uppercase tracking-wider text-white/70">Seconds</span>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <button id="cta-button" class="golden-button mt-8 w-full">
                            Get Instant Free Access to Vagus Skool Now
                        </button>
                        <p class="mt-4 text-sm text-white/80">Join now and receive immediate access to 9 transformative modules.</p>
                    </div>
                </aside>
            </section>
        </div>
    </main>
    <%- include('partials/footer') %>
</body>
</html> 